creator: Balloon Island
descriptionHtml:
Ultimate Jewel is one of the most popular match-three game with an exotic theme and gorgeous effects. The long been waiting next chapter "Ultimate Jewel 2 Tutankhamun" is now available!

This brain teasing game will give you countless hours of fun and satisfaction effects with special designed levels. Reveal the deepest ancient secret of the tomb of Tutankhamun by unlocking rooms and advancing levels; collecting coins in each room to gain stars that you can show off and beat your friends.


Simple rules:

Key will be revealed once all floor tiles are cleared.
Acquire the key by moving it to the bottom to unlock the room.
No time limit, no move limit, absolutely free of charge.


What's new:

Powerful bombs can be made by different formations.
Mixing bombs to create combo effects.
New fancy tile types to either help or block your way.
Maps to assist you navigating the level.
Treasure room and trophy room.
Login facebook to save game score.
Compete with your friends on facebook.
And much more!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
New tiles and levels
Fix volume control issue
Performance improvements
